        <abstract>
            <p>CD’s father has given him £200 to settle his debts.</p>
            <p>He is delighted by a magnificent anonymous gift of a microscope.</p>
            <p>Sees a good deal of the Henslows who are expecting a child soon.</p>
            <p>CD still talks of the "Canary scheme"; he is learning Spanish.</p>
        </abstract>
